This is a package made by Enya Liu for UW BIOST 561 (Spring 2025). This package can generate an adjacency matrix with a partial clique and find a optimal maximal partial clique in the adjacency matrix or graph.

  • The URL to the Pkgdown webpage is: https://enya126.github.io/UWBiost561/

How to install

This package is called UWBiost561. To install, run the following code (in R):

library(devtools)
devtools::install_github("enya126/UWBiost561")
